
= coined by the [[Free Network Movement]]



=Description=

"Wireless communications technology is allowing for the construction of a network in a way that is grassroots, bottom-up, and free from censorship and control. This technology grows steadily more powerful, while continuing to decline in cost. There is freedom on the airwaves, now. We are blanketing the planet with an electromagnetic mesh. We have found the frequency of our salvation. We call this innovation the Mesh Interface for Network Devices."
(http://freenetworkmovement.org/Freenet/Society.html)


